edback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 04, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104toc1665703008287.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/toc1665703008287.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/toc1665703008287.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"toc1665703008287\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n $length\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"toc1665703008287___length_273267\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the length of the specified argument.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"toc1665703008287__topic_d85613e1_d85614e1_d85615e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"toc1665703008287__p_d85616e1_d85617e1_d85618e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$length(Argument)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"toc1665703008287__topic_d56877e1_d56878e1_d56879e1_d56880e1_d56881e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612546e64\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Data Type</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword parmname\">String</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"toc1665703008287__table_d9020e1_d9021e1_d9022e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">String, field, variable, raw data, or function.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"toc1665703008287__topic_d56882e1_d56883e1_d56884e1_d56885e1_d56886e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612546e136\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"toc1665703008287__p_d85625e1_d85626e1_d85627e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$length</span> returns the length of the argument.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"toc1665703008287__topic_d56887e1_d56888e1_d56889e1_d56890e1_d56891e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612546e148\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"toc1665703008287__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"toc1665703008287__topic_d56892e1_d56893e1_d56894e1_d56895e1_d56896e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612546e158\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"toc1665703008287__p_d85637e1_d85638e1_d85639e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$length</span> returns the\n            length of the argument in characters. For raw data, you can use the assignment setting\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iej1741086838875.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iej1741086838875.html\" title=\"Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw.\">$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES</a></code> in case you want to know the\n            byte size.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"toc1665703008287__p_d85640e1_d85641e1_d85642e1\">If <span class=\"keyword parmname\">String</span> contains frame marker, ruler, or character attribute characters, they are ignored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"toc1665703008287__section_gbv_54b_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d612546e184\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$length</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the results of using\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$length</span> with variables of type string, numeric, raw data, and\n               floating-point:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"toc1665703008287__pre_qq4_v4b_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n    float fnum\n    numeric strLen, num, byteLen\n    string strnum, str\n    raw rawdata\nendvariables\n\nnum = -123456\nfnum = -1234.56\nstrnum = \"-1,234.56\"\nstr = \"Hello\"\nrawdata = \"{!{#{%{'\"\nstrLen = $length(num)      ; strLen = 7\nstrLen = $length(fnum)     ; strLen = 8\nstrLen = $length(strnum)   ; strLen = 9\nstrLen = $length(str)      ; strLen = 5\nstrLen = $length(rawdata)  ; strLen = 8, $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0 or is omitted.\nbyteLen= $length(rawdata)  ; byteLen= 4, $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1.</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hqx1699858286844.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$random</a><p>Generate a random string, raw data of a specified length, or a number between 0 and 1.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iej1741086838875.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES</a><p>Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hha1720076228830.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>length (deprecated)</a><p>Return the number of characters in the specified string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532448\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532448\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$length Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 04, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $length Return the length of the specified argument. $length(Argument) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String, field, variable, raw data, or function. Return Values The function $length returns the length of the argument. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $length returns the length of the argument in characters. For raw data, you can use the assignment setting $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES in case you want to know the byte size. If String contains frame marker, ruler, or character attribute characters, they are ignored. Example: Using $length The following example shows the results of using $length with variables of type string, numeric, raw data, and floating-point: variables float fnum numeric strLen, num, byteLen string strnum, str raw rawdata endvariables num = -123456 fnum = -1234.56 strnum = \"-1,234.56\" str = \"Hello\" rawdata = \"{!{#{%{'\" strLen = $length(num) ; strLen = 7 strLen = $length(fnum) ; strLen = 8 strLen = $length(strnum) ; strLen = 9 strLen = $length(str) ; strLen = 5 strLen = $length(rawdata) ; strLen = 8, $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0 or is omitted. byteLen= $length(rawdata) ; byteLen= 4, $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1. Copy Related Links $random Generate a random string, raw data of a specified length, or a number between 0 and 1. $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw. length (deprecated) Return the number of characters in the specified string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}